sections.heading: includes references to
sections.text:
197.352, which was amended and renumbered as 195.305 by action of the

Legislative Assembly. See section 28, chapter 354, Oregon Laws 2007, and

sections 1, 1a and 4, chapter 424, Oregon Laws 2007. The text of 197.353 was not

amended to reflect the amendments or renumbering. Editorial adjustment of

197.353 for the amendments to and renumbering of 197.352 has not been made.
